For Mozzarella Pesto Spread: MIX all ingredients until combined well. SERVE at room temperature. For Creamy Cheddar Spread: BEAT cream cheese in a small bowl until creamy (use an electric mixer on medium). ADD milk gradually, beating until blended well; then add cheddar cheese and red pepper. REFRIGERATE at least 1 hour before serving. For 3-Pepper Cheese Spread: MIX all ingredients and cover. REFRIGERATE at least 1 hour before serving.